    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Engin Üstün</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:147px;\"><a href=\"/File:Engin%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/6/6a/Engin%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn.jpg\" width=\"145\" height=\"187\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Engin%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Engin Üstün</div></div></div> \n<p><b>Engin Üstün</b>,<br />\na Turkish German <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Webmaster\">Webmaster</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and computer chess programmer. \nIn 1995 he started chess programming, began to learn the <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a> programming language to write the engine <a href=\"/EnginMax\" title=\"EnginMax\">EnginMax</a> using the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and later <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>. \nIn 2004, he started to write his new UCI engine <a href=\"/Tornado\" title=\"Tornado\">Tornado</a> from scratch, which is based on <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboards</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=35022\">about WB Tournaments on my Page</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 10, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=50429\">UCI protocol in winboard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, September 24, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30405\">perft and nps speed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30525\">Tornado 3.42 released!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34081\">Tornado and EnginMax available again&#160;!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 30, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37223\">doing lazy exit in eval or better not&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 22, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43771\">using Popcount and Prefetch with SSE4 hardware support</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 19, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Population_Count\" title=\"Population Count\">Population Count</a>, <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">Memory</a>, <a href=\"/SSE4\" title=\"SSE4\">SSE4</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55403\">Tornado webpage is deleted</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 20, 2015</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://tornadochessengine.blogspot.com/\">Tornado Chess</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Engin_%C3%9Cst%C3%BCn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=35022\">about WB Tournaments on my Page</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Engin Üstün</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 10, 2001</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301040059\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6120-0!canonical and t